          <heading>Municipal option to exempt horses and ponies from property taxation</heading>
          <content>
            <p>Sec. 12-81gg. Municipal option to exempt horses and ponies from property taxation.Notwithstanding the provisions of subdivision (68) of section12-81and section12-91, any municipality may, by vote of its legislative body or, in a municipality where the legislative body is a town meeting, by vote of the board of selectmen, exempt from property taxation horses or ponies of any value.
